text: Miejski Klub Sportowy Start Radziejów is a football club from Radziejów, Poland. It was founded in 1948. In 2011, it played in the Polish Fourth League (V level) ==References== * Information about the club on 90minut.pl Category:Association football clubs established in 1948 Category:1948 establishments in Poland Category:Radziejów County Category:Football clubs in Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship
